---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Best Free Antivirus & Security Tools in 2026</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-gray-200">
                <p>Many companies push paid antivirus heavily, but free tools have improved dramatically. In most cases, the free options recommended by techs are more than enough for everyday use. Here are the best ones in 2026.</p>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Top Free Recommendations</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 list-disc pl-6">
                        <li><strong>Windows Defender</strong> – Built into Windows and surprisingly effective for most users.</li>
                        <li><strong>Malwarebytes</strong> – Excellent for on-demand scans and removing stubborn malware.</li>
                        <li><strong>uBlock Origin</strong> – Browser extension that blocks ads and many malware sources.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Important Note</h2>
                    <p>Prevention is much easier than removal. These tools work best when installed <em>before</em> an infection occurs. Safe browsing habits are still your strongest defense.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Need Help Removing an Infection?</h2>
                    <p>If you suspect your PC is already infected, our remote malware removal and cleanup service can get you back up and running safely and quickly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-16">
                <a href="/contact"
                   class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Get Your PC Scanned Today
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
